msgctxt "QL_TreasureHunt_touzoku07_Desc"
msgid ""
"The royal family of Hyrule collected historically\n"
"significant outfits, but they were stolen by a\n"
"bandit named Misko. One of the items stolen\n"
"was the helmet of the Usurper King.\n"
"\n"
"Somewhere in the <1.se_co>Deya Village Ruins<2.re_co>\n"
"is a journal that places the location\n"
"of this treasure..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_TreasureHunt_touzoku07_Finish"
msgid ""
"\"The helm of the self-proclaimed King of\n"
"Shadows is in the swamp of the valley\n"
"of dead trees, south of Dueling Peaks.\"\n"
"\n"
"You found the treasure that was hidden at\n"
"Tobio's Hollow and obtained <1.se_co>Zant's Helmet<2.re_co>!"
msgstr ""

